					<p>We've built and maintained custom content management systems, e-commerce tools, online directories, calendars and more. We are also active in the open source community and contribute to a number of existing software projects.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 made-button">
					<a href="art"><i class="fa fa-lg fa-play-circle"></i> Art</a>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 made-button">
					<a href="technology"><i class="fa fa-lg fa-play-circle"></i> Technology</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
